{"book": 1, "chapter": 49, "sections": [{"type": "heading", "heading": "雅各的遺囑"}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 1, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 雅各叫了他的兒子們來，說：「你們都來聚集，我好把你們日後必遇的事告訴你們。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 1, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 雅各的兒子們，你們要聚集而聽，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "要聽你們父親以色列的話。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 2, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 呂便哪，你是我的長子，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "是我力量強壯的時候生的，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "本當大有尊榮，權力超眾。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 3, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "但你放縱情慾，滾沸如水，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "必不得居首位；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因為你上了你父親的牀，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "污穢了我的榻。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 4, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 西緬和利未是弟兄；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他們的刀劍是殘忍的器具。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 5, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "我的靈啊，不要與他們同謀；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我的心哪，不要與他們聯絡；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "因為他們趁怒殺害人命，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "任意砍斷牛腿大筋。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 6, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "他們的怒氣暴烈可咒；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他們的忿恨殘忍可詛。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我要使他們分居在雅各家裏，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "散住在以色列地中。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 7, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 猶大啊，你弟兄們必讚美你；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你手必掐住仇敵的頸項；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你父親的兒子們必向你下拜。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 8, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 猶大是個小獅子；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "我兒啊，你抓了食便上去。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "你屈下身去，臥如公獅，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "蹲如母獅，誰敢惹你？"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 9, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "圭必不離猶大，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "杖必不離他兩腳之間，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "直等細羅來到，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "萬民都必歸順。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 10, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 猶大把小驢拴在葡萄樹上，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "把驢駒拴在美好的葡萄樹上。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他在葡萄酒中洗了衣服，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "在葡萄汁中洗了袍褂。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 11, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "他的眼睛必因酒紅潤；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他的牙齒必因奶白亮。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 12, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 西布倫必住在海口，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "必成為停船的海口；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他的境界必延到西頓。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 13, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 以薩迦是個強壯的驢，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "臥在羊圈之中。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 14, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "他以安靜為佳，以肥地為美，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "便低肩背重，成為服苦的僕人。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 15, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 但必判斷他的民，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "作以色列支派之一。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 16, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 但必作道上的蛇，路中的虺，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "咬傷馬蹄，使騎馬的墜落於後。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 17, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "耶和華啊，我向來等候你的救恩。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 18, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 迦得必被敵軍追逼，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他卻要追逼他們的腳跟。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 19, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 20, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 亞設之地必出肥美的糧食，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 20, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "且出君王的美味。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 20, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 21, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 拿弗他利是被釋放的母鹿；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 21, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他出嘉美的言語。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 21, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 約瑟是多結果子的樹枝，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "是泉旁多結果的枝子；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他的枝條探出牆外。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 22, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "弓箭手將他苦害，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "向他射箭，逼迫他。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 23, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 24, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "但他的弓仍舊堅硬；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 24, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "他的手健壯敏捷。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 24, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "這是因以色列的牧者，以色列的磐石－"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 24, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "就是雅各的大能者。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 24, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 25, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "你父親的神必幫助你；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 25, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "那全能者必將天上所有的福，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 25, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "地裏所藏的福，以及生產乳養的福，都賜給你。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 25, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 26, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "你父親所祝的福"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 26, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "勝過我祖先所祝的福，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 26, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "如永世的山嶺，至極的邊界；"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 26, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "這些福必降在約瑟的頭上，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 26, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "臨到那與弟兄迥別之人的頂上。"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 26, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 27, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": " 便雅憫是個撕掠的狼，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 27, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "早晨要吃他所抓的，"}]}, {"type": "line-quote", "contents": [{"verseNum": 27, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": "晚上要分他所奪的。」"}]}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 27, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 28, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "這一切是以色列的十二支派；這也是他們的父親對他們所說的話，為他們所祝的福，都是按着各人的福分為他們祝福。"}]}, {"type": "heading", "heading": "雅各的死和埋葬"}, {"type": "paragraph", "contents": [{"verseNum": 28, "hasVerseLabel": false, "verseText": " "}, {"verseNum": 29, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "他又囑咐他們說：「我將要歸到我列祖那裏，你們要將我葬在赫人以弗崙田間的洞裏，與我祖我父在一處， "}, {"verseNum": 30, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "就是在迦南地幔利前、麥比拉田間的洞；那洞和田是亞伯拉罕向赫人以弗崙買來為業，作墳地的。 "}, {"verseNum": 31, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "他們在那裏葬了亞伯拉罕和他妻子撒拉，又在那裏葬了以撒和他的妻子利百加；我也在那裏葬了利亞。 "}, {"verseNum": 32, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "那塊田和田間的洞原是向赫人買的。」 "}, {"verseNum": 33, "hasVerseLabel": true, "verseText": "雅各囑咐眾子已畢，就把腳收在牀上，氣絕而死，歸他列祖那裏去了。"}]}]}